The paper discusses security issues in deep reinforcement learning algorithms, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). Additionally, the paper focuses on the applications of deep RL in various fields such as robotics, control systems, and defense technologies, which are covered by artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and systems and control (cs.SY) sub-categories. Lastly, the paper also discusses mitigation and prevention of intentional attacks against deep RL, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) sub-category.
